OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with some warm evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry with mostly
OL,8,Fclear spells overnight. However, some
OL,9,Fmid to high level cloud will move
OL,10,Fsouthwards during the early hours.
OL,11,FLight winds, but breezier along
OL,12,Fcoasts. Staying mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,15,Fcloud and sunny spells. Temperatures
OL,16,Fwill be lower than of late as a breezy
OL,17,Fonshore wind develops.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
